<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Imminent Auto Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .otp-box {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4caf50;
            background: #292929;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 150px; /* Adjust the size of your logo */
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .details {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #292929;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display:none;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #4caf50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #bbb;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4caf50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        p{
            color:white!important;
        }

        .details > p{
            text-transform: capitalize;
            margin-top: 7px;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function showDetails(){
            const details = document.querySelector(".details");
            if(details){
                details.style.display = "block";
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img style="width:70px;height:70px" src="https://marketplace.crygoca.com/assets/_images/flutterwave-logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>
        <h1 style="color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0;">Imminent Auto Confirmation</h1>


        <p>Dear <strong><%= data.buyerUserName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>This is a reminder that your order <strong># <%= data.checkOutId %></strong> is scheduled for automatic confirmation in <strong>less than <%= timeout %> minutes</strong>.</p>

        <p>The seller has indicated that they have sent the crypto to your provided address. If you have <strong>not received the value</strong>, it is crucial that you take action now.</p>

        <p>Once the system auto-confirms the order, we will <strong>not</strong> be held responsible for any discrepancies. If you believe the seller has <strong>not</strong> fulfilled their obligation, please <strong>immediately</strong> click the button below to dispute the order before auto-confirmation takes effect.</p>

        <a href="<%=disputeUrl %>" target="_blank" class="btn">Dispute Order</a>

        <p>If you have already received the crypto, no further action is required.</p>

        <button class="otp-box" onclick="showDetails()">See more details</button>

        <div class="details">
            <p class="title">Order Details:</p>
            <p><strong>Checkout Reference:</strong> <%= data.checkOutId %></p>
            <p><strong>Crypto</strong>: <div style="display:flex;justify-content: start; align-items: center; gap:10px"><img style="border: 0; font-size: 0; margin: 0; max-width: 100%; padding: 0; padding-left:5px;width: 25px; border-radius: 50%;object-fit: contain;" src="<%= data.cryptoLogo %>" alt="GO"><div style="padding:15px"><%= data.cryptoName %>-(<%= data.cryptoCode %>)</div></div></p>
            <p><strong>Units:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= data.units %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= data.currency %> <%= data.amount %></p>
            <p><strong>Wallet Address:</strong> <%= data.walletAddress %></p>
            <p><strong>Seller:</strong> <%= data.sellerUserName %></p>
            <p><strong>Payment Option:</strong> <%= data.paymentOption %></p>
            <p><strong>Transaction Reference:</strong> <%= data.checkOutId %></p>
            <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= data.date %></p>
        </div>

        <p>For further enquiries, please contact our customer support through the following channels:</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +44-273874848838</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@crygoca.com">support@crygoca.com</a></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Crygoca</strong>.</p>
            <p>The Crygoca Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
